characteristics.name: Capacity
characteristics.value: This model can transport 10 <LEGION> INFANTRY models (each TERMINATOR and JUMP PACK model takes up the space of two other models, and each CULT OF DESTRUCTION model takes up the space of three other models). If the Accursed Phylactery ability has been selected, then this model may only transport six models.

modifiers.value: This model can transport 6 <LEGION> INFANTRY models (each TERMINATOR and JUMP PACK model takes up the space of two other models, and each CULT OF DESTRUCTION model takes up the space of three other models).
